Program: Discovery
Title: Ethnic cleansing
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxdn
Last Broadcast Date: 21 May 1999
Genetic weapons - biology and ethnic cleansing. From the British giving Native American Indians blankets covered with smallpox to genetic engineering which can be designed to target biological weapons at ethnic groups; a look at how science has in the past and could in the future be used to make ethnic weapons. Show less